ider.com%2Fintergenerational-age-gap-friendship-mother-daughter-mentorship-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Court%20Declines%20Nikhil%20Gupta's%20Motion%20on%20Producing%20Case%20Materials%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F13160636%2FSDNY-courthouses.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20US%20federal%20court%20on%20Thursday%20(January%2011)%20denied%20Nikhil%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20motion%20to%20compel%20the%20American%20government%20to%20produce%20materials%20relating%20to%20his%20alleged%20murder-for-hire%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20has%20alleged%20that%20Gupta%20was%20part%20of%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20assassinate%20Gurpatwant%20Pannun%2C%20a%20pro-Khalistan%20lawyer%20and%20US%20citizen%2C%20on%20US%20soil%20and%20that%20he%20was%20engaged%20in%20this%20mission%20by%20an%20Indian%20government%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPTI%20reported%20US%20District%20Judge%20Victor%20Marrero%20as%20saying%20on%20Thursday%20that%20the%20court%20was%20persuaded%20by%20the%20US%20government%E2%80%99s%20argument%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribuneindia.com%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fus-court-denies-guptas-plea-for-defence-material-580836%5C%22%3EGupta%20did%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20right%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20the%20case%20materials%20and%20evidence%20he%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20earlier%20report%20by%20the%20news%20agency%2C%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20attorney%20argued%20that%20his%20lawyers%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20%E2%80%93%20where%20he%20has%20been%20jailed%20since%20June%20%E2%80%93%20were%20unable%20to%20secure%20his%20rights%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20information%20on%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20defence%20counsel%20present%20in%20Prague%20has%20no%20evidence%20or%20other%20case%20materials%20other%20than%20the%20bare%20indictment%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20counsel%20in%20the%20US%20Jeff%20Chabrowe%20told%20the%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theweek.in%2Fnews%2Fworld%2F2024%2F01%2F11%2Fpannun-case-us-objects-to-providing-defence-material-to-nikhil-gupta-till-his-appearance-in-ny-court.html%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20PTI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChabrowe%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CMost%20critically%2C%20the%20defendant%20continues%20(to%20be)%20interrogated%20by%20US%20officials%2C%20after%20the%20indictment%2C%20where%20his%20uninformed%20counsel%20has%20no%20ability%20to%20secure%20his%20rights.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccordingly%2C%20this%20court%20should%20order%20the%20government%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20defence%20discovery%20request%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20request%20for%20%E2%80%98discovery%E2%80%99%20refers%20to%20a%20request%20to%20the%20prosecution%20to%20share%20certain%20case%20materials%20and%20evidence%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao%2Fjustice-101%2Fdiscovery%5C%22%3Eahead%20of%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistrict%20Judge%20Marrero%20had%20on%20Monday%20(January%208)%20given%20the%20government%20three%20days%20to%20respond%20to%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20it%20was%20ready%20to%20produce%20discovery%20upon%20Gupta%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20in%20court%20and%20that%20he%20was%20not%20entitled%20to%20discovery%20until%20then%2C%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20denied%20that%20Gupta%20was%20repeatedly%20interrogated%20by%20US%20officials%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%2C%20adding%20that%20Gupta%20and%20law%20enforcement%20authorities%20had%20only%20met%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGupta%20voluntarily%20spoke%20to%20authorities%20in%20their%20first%20meeting%20and%20declined%20to%20be%20interviewed%20upon%20their%20second%20meeting%2C%20PTI%20cited%20the%20US%20government%20a