0Therefore%2C%20I%20think%20interest%20rates%20will%20stay%20higher%2C%20longer%20than%20all%20of%20us%20had%20hoped%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E3.%20%26quot%3BWhether%20it%20be%20the%20Middle%20East%20situation%2C%20whether%20it's%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20situation%2C%20whether%20it's%20China%20and%20Taiwan%2C%20there's%20just%20a%20lot%20of%20uncertainty%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20places%20in%20the%20world%20today.%20I'm%20just%20cautious%20right%20now%2C%20and%20I%20am%20concerned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E4.%20%26quot%3BWe%20thrive%20at%20KKR%20on%20uncertainty.%20We%20like%20the%20time%20when%20markets%20are%20out%20of%20kilter%20because%20we%20invest%20around%20the%20world.%20By%20doing%20that%2C%20we%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20lean%20in%20where%20we%20see%20a%20part%20of%20the%20market%20that%20happens%20to%20be%20very%20strong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E5.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20looks%20smart%20when%20markets%20are%20going%20up.%20Just%20ride%20the%20wave%20and%20you'll%20do%20just%20fine.%20The%20key%20for%20a%20good%20investor%20is%20how%20do%20they%20do%20in%20downturns%3F%20George's%20view%20and%20my%20view%20has%20always%20been%2C%20lean%20in.%26quot%3B%20(Kravis%20was%20referring%20to%20one%20of%20his%20cofounders%2C%20George%20Roberts.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E6.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20forget%3A%20Everything%20that%20goes%20up%2C%20comes%20down%2C%20and%20everything%20that's%20down%20will%20come%20back%20up%20at%20some%20point.%20If%20you%20think%20we're%20going%20into%20a%20bad%20downturn%2C%20just%20be%20prepared%2C%20okay%3F%20Don't%20sit%20and%20say%2C%20'Wow%2C%20where%20did%20this%20come%20from%3F%20You've%20got%20to%20prepare%20yourself.%20The%20other%20thing%20is%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20when%20you're%20in%20a%20downturn%2C%20you%20see%20cracks%20in%20companies.%20You%20see%20that%20things%20aren't%20quite%20as%20good%20as%20what%20a%20strong%20economy%20and%20a%20strong%20market%20will%20mask.%20All%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20you%20look%20at%20it%20and%20say%2C%20'Wow%2C%20there's%20opportunity%20here.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E7.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20congratulate%20us%20when%20we%20make%20an%20investment.%20Any%20fool%20can%20make%20an%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20easy%2C%20just%20pay%20enough.%20The%20harder%20part%20is%20what%20do%20you%20do%20to%20create%20value%3F%20That's%20our%20focus%2C%20like%20a%20laser.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E8.%20%26quot%3BI%20like%20to%20think%20of%20corporations%20very%20much%20as%20an%20evolving%20entity.%20They%20change.%20Think%20of%20a%20movie%2C%20which%20is%20made%20up%20of%20a%20series%20of%20still%20photos.%20You%20as%20the%20director%20of%20the%20movie%20can%20make%20it%20go%20any%20which%20way%20you%20want.%20Well%2C%20that's%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20how%20we%20invest.%20If%20we%20are%20able%20to%20take%20control%20of%20a%20company%2C%20or%20even%20have%20a%20very%20large%20position%20in%20a%20company%2C%20and%20work%20with%20a%20management%20team%2C%20can%20we%20make%20that%20business%20a%20better%20business%3F%20That's%20really%20our%20focus.%20Too%20many%20people%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20are%20focused%20on%20one%20still%20photo%20in%20that%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E9.%20%26quot%3BI've%20been%20called%20worse%20things.%20But%20it's%20hard%20to%20shake%20that.%20The%20title%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20really%20had%20an%20impact.%20We%20are%20no%20more%20barbarians%20than%20the%20man%20in%20the%20moon.%20We%20will%20not%20do%20a%20deal%20if%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20said%2C%20'Go%20away.%20We%20have%20no%20interest%20in%20dealing%20with%20you.'%20We%20don't%20take%20positions%20in%20companies%20and%20go%20in%20and%20rattle%20the%20saber%20and%20say%20we're%20going%20to%20throw%20your%20board%20out.%20That's%20just%20not%20what%20we%20do.%26quot%3B%20(He%20was%20bemoaning%20the%20choice%20of%20%26quot%3BBarbarians%20at%20the%20Gate%26quot%3B%20as%20the%20title%20of%20a%20book%20he%20appears%20in.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10.%20%26quot%3BI%20say%20to%20my%20children%20and%20grandchildren%2C%20take%20one%20sentence%20out%20of%20your%20vocabulary%20and%20that's%20very%20simply%2C%20'I%20wish%20I%20had.'%20I%20hate%20when%20I%20hear%2C%20'Oh%2C%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20done%20this%20or%20I%20wish%20I%20had%20gone%20there.'%20Okay%2C%20you%20could%20have%20done%20it.%20We%20live%20in%20a%20free%20world.%20We%20live%20in%20a%20wonderful%20country%20in%20America%2C%20and%20you%20can%20make%20mistakes%20and%20try%20again.%20So%20I'm%20very%20big%20on%20pushing%20people%20to%20give%20it%20a%20try.%20Don't%20be%20afraid.%20Don't%20just%20talk%20about%20it%3A%20'Oh%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20this.%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20that.'%20No.%20Go%20do%20it.%20Both%20feet%20in%20and%20be%20dedicated.%20And%20if%20it%20doesn't%20work%2C%20okay.%20Pick%20yourself%20up%2C%20go%20try%20it%20again.%20Don't%20be%20afraid%20to%20fail.%20There's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20failure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkkr-kravis-private-equity-inflation-rates-recession-economy-israel-ukraine-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705145401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F55f03dc09dd7cc14008b901a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fkkr-kravis-private-equity-inflation-rates-recession-economy-israel-ukraine-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22KKR's%20billionaire%20cofounder%2C%20Henry%20Kravis%2C%20compared%20companies%20to%20movies%20and%20urged%20people%20to%20take%20chances%20even%20if%20they%20might%20fail.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tmohamed%40insider.com%20(Theron%20Mohamed)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fkkr-kravis-private-equity-inflation-rates-recession-economy-israel-ukraine-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A