caption%3EMy%20Tesla%20Model%203%2C%20sufficiently%20dirty%20from%20winter%20roads%20in%20Michigan%2C%20sitting%20at%20a%20Supercharger%3Cp%3ENora%20Naughton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20had%20to%20charge%20my%20Model%203%20four%20times%20in%20five%20days.%20One%20of%20those%20trips%20to%20the%20charger%20was%20a%20pointless%2015%20minutes%20where%20I%20just%20charged%20to%20what%20I%20had%20started%20when%20I%20left%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20charged%20once%20in%20about%20five%20days%20of%20driving.%20I%20also%20didn't%20drive%20as%20far%20as%20you.%20And%20it%20was%20warmer%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20than%20Detroit.%20Do%20you%20think%20that%20was%20the%20big%20decider%20here%3F%20Full%20disclosure%3A%20I%20borrowed%20two%20Model%203s%20from%20two%20friends.%20(Thank%20you%20Lennie%20and%20Bruce!)%20I%20had%20one%20for%20three%20days%20and%20another%20for%20two%20days%2C%20so%20I%20survived%20by%20giving%20one%20car%20back%20(to%20Lennie)%20with%20not%20much%20juice%20left%20in%20it.%20Sorry%20mate.%20Then%20I%20charged%20Bruce's%20vehicle%20once%20at%20a%20Tesla%20Supercharger%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I'd%20say%20the%20two%20cars%20probably%20helped%20you%20out%2C%20but%20overall%20I%20think%20I%20struggled%20more%20here%20because%20I%20drive%20a%20lot%20more%20in%20the%20Detroit%20area%20(everything%20in%20the%20Midwest%20is%20far%20apart)%20and%20we%20had%20freezing%20weather%20the%20whole%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20cold%20weather%20hampered%20both%20of%20our%20charging%20experiences%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20rental%20in%20my%20driveway%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659eb8d4ec62ab5daf8243e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20Model%203%20rental%20in%20my%20driveway%3Cp%3ENora%20Naughton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20You%20had%20real%20challenges%20with%20the%20weather%2C%20right%3F%20Deal%20killers%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDefinitely%20deal%20killers%20for%20me.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-ev-batteries-drain-faster-dont-last-long-cold-weather-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecold%20weather's%20effect%20on%20the%20battery%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20I%20was%20still%20spending%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20time%20chasing%20range.%20I%20never%20had%20a%20moment%20where%20I%20couldn't%20find%20a%20charger%20when%20I%20needed%20one%2C%20but%20all%20of%20the%20Supercharger%20stations%20here%20are%20tucked%20away.%20What%20about%20you%3F%20How%20was%20your%20one%20charging%20experience%3F%20How%20long%20were%20you%20there%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Even%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bcold%26quot%3B%20(California%20cold%20to%20be%20clear)%20was%20a%20factor%20here.%20When%20I%20got%20into%20the%20Model%203%20during%20the%20mornings%2C%20the%20battery%20had%20lost%20some%20power%20overnight.%20There%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bcold%26quot%3B%20icon%20near%20the%20battery%20level%20icon.%20It%20did%20make%20me%20wonder%20about%20you%20in%20Detroit%20in%20the%20winter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ENeither%20of%20us%20had%20to%20wait%20to%20charge%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Teslas%20parked%20at%20Supercharger%20stations%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a19ae9dcdb354a985747ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETeslas%20parked%20at%20Supercharger%20stations%20in%20San%20Francisco%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20might%20be%20one%20part%20of%20American%20society%20where%20the%20roles%20have%20flipped.%20Californians%20are%20pretty%20sunny%20friendly%20people%2C%20compared%20to%20gruff%20New%20Yorkers.%20But%20at%20Supercharger%20stations%2C%20it's%20down%20to%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20Tesla%20Supercharger%20trip%20involved%20no%20nice%20interactions%20with%20other%20humans.%20They%20were%20all%20sitting%20in%20their%20cars%20staring%20at%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20about%209%20cars%20getting%20charged%20and%20about%206%20or%207%20spots%20open%20when%20I%20got%20there%2C%20so%20I%20did%20not%20have%20to%20wait.%20A%20couple%20of%20the%20charging%20stations%20had%20big%20crosses%20on%20them%2C%20which%20I%20assume%20meant%20that%20they%20were%20not%20working.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20at%20about%2055%20miles%20left%2C%20and%20after%20about%2010%20minutes%20I%20was%20up%20to%20115%20miles%20charge.%20The%20session%20cost%20about%20%247.50%20which%20was%20charged%20automatically%20to%20my%20friend's%20account%20at%20Tesla%20(I%20repaid%20him).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20heard%20those%20California%20stations%20can%20get%20busy%20so%20I'm%20glad%20you%20didn't%20have%20to%20wait.%20The%20Supercharger%20I%20went%20to%20in%20Detroit%20was%20the%20busiest%2C%20and%20I%20nabbed%20the%20last%20spot%20at%2010%3A30%20pm%2C%20but%20it's%20rare%20to%20ever%20see%20any%20EVs%20lined%20up%20at%20chargers%20here.%20I%20also%20didn't%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20charging.%20It%20was%20free%20with%20my%20Tesla%20rental%2C%20which%20saved%20me%20money%20given%20how%20much%20I%20had%20to%20charge!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20had%20different%20experiences%20with%20range%20anxiety%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close-up%20of%20Tesla%20Model%203%20charging%20at%20a%20Tesla%20Supercharger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1995f6979d737182301e1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClose-up%20of%20Tesla%20Model%203%20charging%20at%20a%20Tesla%20Supercharger%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20think%20you%20had%20range%20on%20the%20brain%20more%20than%20me%3F%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Some%20of%20it%20might%20be%20my%20previous%20EV%20experiences.%20When%20I%20had%20a%20Chevy%20Bolt%20for%202%20weeks%20in%202019%2C%20I%20had%20a%20few%20moments%20on%20a%20road%20trip%20where%20I%20really%20was%20almost%20stranded%20without%20power.%20That%20past%20range%20anxiety%20loomed%20large%2C%20and%20I%20was%20constantly%20trying%20to%20avoid%20a%20repeat.%20I%20also%20just%20watched%20my%20battery%20drain%20every%20day%20due%20to%20the%20cold%2C%20and%20that%20was%20really%20disheartening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Programming%20note%3A%20Tesla%20just%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Fautos-transportation%2Ftesla-lowers-range-estimates-us-regulators-tighten-vehicle-test-rules-2024-01-09%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3E%20lowered%20the%20estimated%20ranges%20for%20most%20of%20its%20vehicles%20recently%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20noticed%20the%20lower%20battery%20charge%20on%20those%20cold%20mornings.%20I%20think%20that%20would%20have%20weighed%20more%20on%20my%20mind%20had%20I%20been%20commuting%20regularly%20and%20absolutely%20had%20to%20be%20somewhere%20else%20far%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20work%20from%20home%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20extracurricular%20activities%20(I'm%20downtown%20at%20least%20two%20nights%20a%20week)%20and%20I%20pick%20up%20my%20kid%20from%20daycare%20every%20day%2C%20which%20is%20a%207-mile%20round%20trip.%20I%20was%20constantly%20doing%20mileage%20math.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20access%20to%20Superchargers%20was%20about%20the%20same%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20at%20a%20charger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659ebcebec62ab5daf8246ec%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20my%20many%20stops%20at%20Tesla%20Superchargers%20during%20my%20five-day%20rental%3Cp%3ENora%20Naughton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20bar%20is%20gas%20stations%2C%20right%3F%20I%20have%20two%20or%20three%20gas%20stations%20within%20about%20a%20five-minute%20drive%20from%20my%20home.%20Always%20open%2C%20always%20takes%20five%20minutes%20to%20fill%20up.%20Compared%20with%20that%2C%20finding%20an%20EV%20charging%20station%20is%20still%20a%20relative%20pain%20in%20the%20butt%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20which%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yeah%20if%20we're%20using%20gas%20stations%20as%20the%20bar%2C%20I%20live%20close%20to%20a%20big%20highway%20exit%20with%20four%20or%20five%20big%20gas%20stations.%20I%20can%20throw%20a%20stone%20and%20hit%20a%20pump%20from%20my%20driveway.%20Conversely%2C%20the%20only%20Supercharger%20in%20(reasonable)%20driving%20distance%20from%20my%20house%20was%20a%20town%20over%2C%20about%20a%2015%20minute%20drive.%20Interesting%20that%20you%20had%20basically%20the%20same%20experience%20with%20your%20closest%20Supercharger%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Model%203%20turned%20more%20heads%20in%20Detroit%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20Hertz%20rental%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659eb4a06979d7371821fe1f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20Model%203%20Hertz%20rental%3Cp%3ENora%20Naughton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20didn't%20get%20anyone%20stopping%20to%20ask%20me%20about%20the%20Model%203s%20I%20drove.%20In%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20the%20EV%20driving%20experience%20felt%20oddly%20unspecial.%20In%20a%2015-minute%20drive%20back%20from%20Bruce's%20house%20to%20mine%2C%20I%20passed%20more%20than%2020%2C%20most%20of%20which%20were%20Teslas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20one%20street%20in%20my%20town%2C%20which%20was%20two%20blocks%20long%2C%20I%20drove%20by%20nine%20EVs%20parked%20in%20driveways%20%E2%80%94%20three%20of%20those%20homes%20had%20solar%20panels%20on%20the%20roof.%20It%20did%20not%20feel%20special%20or%20ground-breaking%20to%20be%20driving%20an%20EV%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EEven%20though%20Teslas%20have%20definitely%20become%20more%20commonplace%20here%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20I%20still%20got%20stopped%20plenty%20of%20times%20by%20strangers%20who%20wanted%20to%20know%20what%20a%20Tesla%20was%20like.%20It%20was%20a%20big%20conversation%20piece%20among%20friends%2C%20too%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20have%20never%20been%20in%20an%20electric%20car%2C%20let%20alone%20driven%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20to%20ask%20this%2C%20given%20Elon%20Musk's%20behavior.%20Was%20anyone%20not%20into%20Teslas%20specifically%20due%20to%20Musk's%20rep%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Yes%2C%20Musk%20definitely%20came%20up%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20dislike%20Tesla%2C%20and%20some%20of%20the%20people%20who%20would%20stop%20me%20actually%20would%20ask%20what%20I%20thought%20of%20Elon%20Musk%20rather%20than%20what%20I%20thought%20of%20the%20car.%20I%20always%20tell%20them%20he's%20an%20interesting%20character%20to%20follow!%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIt's%20still%20a%20tricky%20equation%20when%20deciding%20if%20we%20could%20own%20one%20full-time%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tesla%20Model%203%20outside%20a%20house%20in%20San%20Francisco%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a1988f6979d737182300b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETesla%20Model%203%20outside%20a%20house%20in%20San%20Francisco%3Cp%3EAlistair%20Barr%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20a%20%24100%20deposit%20on%20a%20Cybertruck.%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20getting%20that%2C%20but%20I'm%20low%20on%20the%20list%20so%20I%20have%20along%20time%20to%20think%20about%20it.%20With%20my%20solar%20panels%20and%20the%20way%20I%20live%20and%20work%20%E2%80%93%20from%20home%20a%20lot%20%E2%80%93%20it%20would%20make%20financial%20sense%20to%20have%20one%20of%20our%20family%20cars%20be%20an%20EV.%20I%20am%20wasting%20the%20opportunity%20to%20save%20money%20with%20my%20solar%20panels%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20general%20I%20would%20love%20to%20have%20an%20EV%20if%20I%20could%20justify%20one.%20They're%20fun%20to%20drive%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felectric-car-vs-gas-cost-charging-loan-maintenance-study-2022-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20cheaper%20to%20maintain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20let's%20face%20it%2C%20a%20status%20symbol.%20Consider%20as%20well%20the%20environmental%20benefits%20and%20it%20all%20adds%20up%20for%20me%20%E2%80%93%20until%20I%20look%20at%20the%20miles%20I%20drive%20a%20week%20and%20the%20temps%20I%20deal%20with%20from%20November%20to%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYeah%2C%20that's%20a%20huge%20obstacle.%20So%2C%20I%20have%20my%20Subaru%20back%20now%2C%20and%20I%20have%20to%20fill%20up%20with%20gas%20again.%20That's%20a%20more%20expensive%20proposition%20in%20California%20compared%20to%20Detroit.%20According%20to%20AAA%2C%20the%20average%20price%20of%20regular%20gas%20in%20California%20was%20%244.63%20in%20early%20December%20during%20my%20test%20drives.%20The%20average%20in%20Michigan%20was%20%242.99%20at%20that%20time.%20With%20an%2018.5%20gallon%20gas%20tank%20on%20my%20Outback%2C%20that's%20%2487%20to%20fill%20up.%20The%20same%20fillup%20in%20Michigan%20would%20cost%20%2455.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20have%20to%20admit%20when%20I%20pulled%20my%20Subaru%20Crosstrek%20back%20on%20the%20road%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20I%20relished%20that%20smoother%20ride%20after%20five%20days%20of%20one-pedal%20driving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAB%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That's%20funny%20because%20I%20felt%20differently%20getting%20back%20into%20my%20Subaru.%20(We're%20both%20huge%20Subaru%20fans.%20I%20love%20my%20Outback%20so%20much.)%20But%20I%20was%20struck%20by%20the%20noise%20after%20getting%20back%20in%20the%20car.%20In%20comparison%2C%20the%20Model%203%20is%20a%20lot%20smoother%20and%20quieter.%20After%20a%20week%20of%20driving%20this%20EV%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20this%20is%20now%20the%20way%20cars%20should%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENN%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThat's%20such%20an%20interesting%20takeaway.%20I%20think%20the%20wind%20noise%20in%20my%20Model%203%20prevented%20me%20from%20having%20that%20experience.%20My%20Crosstrek%20was%20decidedly%20quieter%20since%20there%20wasn't%20wind%20flapping%20in%20my%20ear%20at%20all%20moments.%20But%20I%20did%20miss%20that%20lurch%20forward%20on%20the%20highway%20on-ramp.%20Ah%2C%20instant%20torque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-driving-charging-silicon-valley-vs-detroit-compared-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705144981000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a19f4fdcdb354a98574bee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-driving-charging-silicon-valley-vs-detroit-compared-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20set%20out%20to%20learn%20about%20regional%20divides%20for%20EVs%20by%20driving%20a%20Tesla%20Model%203%20in%20San%20Franc