www.cedu.niu.edu%2Fcahe%2Fabout%2Ffaculty%2Fsuzanne-degges-white.shtml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESuzanne%20Degges-White%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20licensed%20counselor%20and%20professor%20at%20Northern%20Illinois%20University%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDegges-White%20said%20people%20in%20unhealthy%20relationships%20can%20experience%20several%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fstress-definition%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ephysical%20symptoms%20of%20stress%20and%20anxiety%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20She%20shared%20five%20common%20ways%20your%20health%20can%20be%20impacted%20when%20you%20feel%20unsafe%20or%20unheard%20in%20a%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3EYou%20get%20stomach%20aches%2C%20not%20butterflies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20butterflies%20are%20common%20early%20on%20in%20relationships%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20there's%20a%20big%20difference%20between%20excited%20jitteriness%20and%20more%20serious%20stomach%20pains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20some%20people%2C%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-improve-gut-health-with-food-full-meals-dietitian-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edigestive%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20the%20first%20kind%20of%20red%20alert%20sign%26quot%3B%20that%20something%20isn't%20right%20in%20the%20relationship%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20your%20relationship%20is%20not%20good%20for%20you%2C%20you're%20not%20going%20to%20feel%20those%20butterflies%2C%26quot%3B%20Degges-White%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20feel%20somersaults%20and%20feel%20ill.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Your%20skin%20feels%20itchy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20and%20depression%20can%20lead%20to%20skin%20burning%20and%20itching%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D95d6e715d499db7de59