your%20legs%20are%20heavy%2C%20or%20you%20might%20start%20having%20foot%20pain%20because%20you%20can't%20walk%20another%20mile%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFatigue%20and%20lack%20of%20motivation%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fwhat-is-depression%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esymptoms%20of%20depression%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20can%20be%20caused%20by%20environmental%20factors%20such%20as%20feeling%20stuck%20in%20a%20draining%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20You%20literally%20feel%20suffocated%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20around%20someone%20who%20makes%20you%20feel%20emotionally%20or%20physically%20unsafe%20during%20arguments%2C%20Degges-White%20said%20your%20body%20can%20respond%20by%20entering%20panic%20mode.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20feel%20like%20your%20chest%20is%20constricted%20like%20you%20can't%20breathe%20when%20you're%20around%20someone%20who%20is%20really%20dragging%20you%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20psychologically%20you're%20thinking%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20get%20some%20space%20from%20this%20person.%20I%20need%20some%20air.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Ffight-flight-freeze-fawn%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFight%2C%20flight%2C%20freeze%2C%20or%20fawn%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20responses%20to%20stressful%20situations%2C%20some%20of%20which%20involve%20heavier%20breathing%20or%20panic%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphysical-signs-relationship-affect-bad-for-health-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705142521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a19395dcdb354a98573f6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%