m%2Fnational%2Fstory-indian-army-bharti-agniveer-apply-india-preparation-for-major-changes-in-the-agnipath-scheme-8758101.html%5C%22%3Etalk%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20insisting%20on%2050%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Agniveer%20recruits%20being%20absorbed%20as%20permanent%20last%20year%2C%20but%20analysts%20say%2C%20the%20political%20establishment%20did%20not%20finally%20come%20around%20to%20it%2C%20as%20it%20would%20have%20meant%20a%20significant%20walk%20back%20from%20the%20announcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20stories%20based%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fauthor%2Fmanash-pratim-bhuyan%2F%5C%22%3Eexcerpts%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20book%20were%20also%20published%20by%20news%20agency%20PTI%20in%20December%20in%20the%20form%20of%20five%20news%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fagnipath-scheme-bolt-out-of-the-blue-navy-air-force-former-army-chief-naravane-memoirs%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Scheme%20Was%20%E2%80%98Bolt%20Out%20of%20the%20Blue%E2%80%99%20for%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%3A%20Former%20Army%20Chief%20Naravane%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20chapters%20of%20the%20book%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20while%20some%20chapters%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20Naravane%20wrote%20that%20when%20he%20was%20first%20informed%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%9Cit%20was%20more%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20short-service%20option%20at%20the%20soldier%20level.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20was%20considering%20this%20proposal%2C%20but%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20applicability.%20In%20the%20PMO%20formulation%2C%20not%20only%20should%20the%20complete%20intake%20of%20the%20year%20be%20short-service%20based%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fagnipath-to-galwan-clash-ex-army-chief-general-naravanes-big-revelations-in-memoirs-yet-to-be-released%5C%22%3E%20writes.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20become%20a%20tri-service%20matter%2C%20it%20now%20fell%20on%20the%20CDS%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20to%20take%20the%20proposal%20forward%2C%20albeit%20with%20the%20Army%20remaining%20the%20lead%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20were%20taken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20learnt%20that%20the%20portions%20relating%20to%20the%20revelations%20about%20the%20Agnipath%20scheme%20are%20being%20reviewed%20by%20the%20defence%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20release%20of%20the%20excerpts%20on%20the%20Agniveer%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1737058915341230091%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%257Ctwcamp%255Etweetembed%257Ctwterm%255E1737058915341230091%257Ctwgr%255E84b93666bdab42806d754c6f436f7db89b977168%257Ctwcon%255Es1_%26ref_url%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fthewire.in%252Fbooks%252Fagnipath-to-galwan-clash-ex-army-chief-general-naravanes-big-revelations-in-memoirs-yet-to-be-released%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20accused%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cbulldozing%E2%80%9D%20the%20scheme.%20The%20statement%20said%20that%20General%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20memoirs%20%E2%80%9Cconfirmed%20what%20had%20been%20commonly%20believed%20when%20the%20Agnipath%2FAgniveer%20scheme%20was%20bulldozed%20through%20without%20meaningful%20consultations%20with%20those%20who%20were%20being%20directly%20impacted%20by%20such%20a%20disastrous%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20revelations%20in%20the%20upcoming%20book%2C%20according%20to%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20include%20Naravane%20narrating%20about%20the%20night%20of%20August%2031%2C%202020%2C%20following%20a%20tense%20situation%20arising%20out%20of%20Chinese%20PLA%20moving%20tanks%20and%20troops%20in%20Rechin%20La%20mountain%20pass%20on%20the%20Line%20of%20Actual%20Control%20(LAC)%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20conveyed%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20RM%20(Raksha%20Mantri)%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20which%20he%20did%2C%20by%20about%202230%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20from%20the%20memoirs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Jo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20author%2C%20General%20Naravane%2C%20when%20asked%20about%20the%20final%20release%20date%20for%20the%20book%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20we%20should%20%E2%80%9Ccheck%20with%20publishers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3EWe%20carefully%20review%20all%20our%20books%20to%20ensure%20quality%20content%20and%20this%20process%20may%20impact%20publishing%20timelines%20based%20on%20the%20necessary%20work%20involved.%20As%20part%20of%20this%20editorial%20process%2C%20we%20are%20scheduled%20to%20publish%20General%20M.M.%20Naravane%E2%80%99s%20book%