time.%20%E2%80%9CAlong%20with%20profits%2C%20we%20also%20incur%20losses%20sometimes.%20Last%20year%2C%20we%20faced%20losses%20worth%20Rs%2027%20lakh.%20I%20was%20receiving%20complaints%20of%20low%20yield.%20When%20I%20checked%20the%20machinery%2C%20I%20found%20out%20there%20was%20a%20thin%20hair%20size%20leakage%20that%20contaminated%20the%20spawns%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSometimes%2C%20I%20get%20discouraged%20by%20such%20situations%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20quitting.%20But%20then%20I%20look%20back%20at%20my%20journey%20and%20I%20feel%20overwhelmed%20to%20have%20come%20so%20far.%20I%20have%20a%20commerce%20background%20and%20the%20first%20time%20I%20saw%20a%20test%20tube%20was%20during%20my%20training.%20Such%20small%20achievements%20motivate%20me%20to%20strive%20for%20the%20success%20of%20my%20company.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20now%20I%C2%A0do%20not%20keep%20a%20plan%20B%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShanker%20has%20also%20been%20conferred%20with%20Progressive%20%26amp%3B%20Innovative%20Farmer%20awards%20by%20the%20Rajasthan%20government%20in%202019%20and%20Innovative%20Agricultural%20Startup%20by%20the%20Startup%20India%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmasshree%20Pande.%20All%20images%3A%20Shanker%20Meena.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705071179000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D338206%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wondering%20how%20to%20start%20a%20mushroom%20business%3F%20Rajasthan's%20Shanker%20Meena%20founded%20'Jeevan%20Mushrooms'%2C%20a%20successful%20mushroom%20spawns'%20manufacturing%20unit%20in%20his%20garage.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338206%2Fhow-to-start-a-mushroom-business-rajasthan-mba-dropout-jeevan-success-story%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20Response%20to%20South%20Africa's%20Gaza%20Genocide%20Case%20at%20ICJ%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12201105%2Fimage-1733.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Israel%20on%20Friday%20rejected%20as%20false%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgrossly%20distorted%E2%80%9D%20accusations%20brought%20by%20South%20Africa%20at%20the%20International%20Court%20of%20Justice%20(ICJ)%20that%20its%20military%20operation%20in%20Gaza%20is%20a%20state-led%20genocide%20campaign%20against%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20argued%20that%20it%20was%20acting%20in%20self-defence%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20was%20fighting%20Hamas%2C%20not%20the%20Palestinian%20population.%20Israel%20urged%20the%20ICJ%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%20as%20groundless%20and%20reject%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20request%20to%20order%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20offensive%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisrael-counter-genocide-accusations-world-court-2024-01-12%2F%5C%22%3Eas%20reported%20by%20Reuters.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20Israel%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fshaw-south-africa-cherry-picked-comments-by-israeli-politicians%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20lawyer%20Malcolm%20Shaw%20as%20saying%20that%20South%20Africa%20presented%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdistorted%20picture%E2%80%9D%20of%20comments%20made%20by%20Israeli%20politicians%20on%20the%20war%20in%20order%20to%20establish%20%E2%80%98genocidal%20intent%E2%80%99%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20produce%20random%20quotes%20which%20are%20not%20in%20conformity%20with%20government%20policy%20is%20misleading%20at%20best%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-3%5C%22%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20South%20Africa%20told%20the%20top%20UN%20court%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20aerial%20and%20ground%20offensive%20%E2%80%93%20which%20killed%20almost%2024%2C000%20people%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza%20health%20authorities%20%E2%80%93%20aimed%20to%20bring%20about%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20destruction%20of%20the%20population%E2%80%9D%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Reuters%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20data-testid%3D%5C%22paragraph-4%5C%22%3EHowever%2C%20Israel%20rejected%20these%20accusations%2C%20saying%20it%20respected%20international%20law%20and%20had%20a%20right%20to%20defend%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2Fliveblog%2F2024%2F1%2F12%2Flive-israels-response-to-south-africas-genocide-case-at-the-icj%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Galit%20Raguan%2C%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20international%20justice%20division%20at%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20Justice%20Ministry%2C%20blamed%20Hamas%20for%20the%20high%20civilian%20toll%20in%20Gaza%20and%20said%20that%20Israel%20had%20not%20bombed%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20appalling%20suffering%20of%20civilians%2C%20both%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%2C%20is%20first%20and%20foremost%20the%20result%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20strategy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Reuters%20reported%20Tal%20Becker%2C%20the%20Israeli%20foreign%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20legal%20adviser%2C%20as%20saying%20in%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGilad%20Noam%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20attorney%20general%20for%20international%20affairs%2C%20argued%20against%20the%20use%20of%20provisional%20measures%2C%20citing%20reasons%20such%20as%20Hamas%20being%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20Israel%20and%20other%20countries.%20As%20per%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20he%20also%20pointed%20to%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20involvement%20in%20a%20large-scale%20terrorist%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChristopher%20Staker%2C%20an%20international%20lawyer%20previously%20on%20the%20criminal%20tribunal%20for%20the%20former%20Yugoslavia%2C%20claimed%20Israel%20had%20facilitated%20humanitarian%20aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20ruling%20on%20South%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20urgent%20request%20for%20provisional%20measures%2C%20either%20in%20favour%20or%20against%2C%20is%20expected%20from%20the%20court%20later%20this%20month%2C%20news%20reports%20said.%20It%20will%20not%20rule%20at%20that%20time%20on%20the%20genocide%20accusations.%20Those%20proceedings%20could%20take%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705070555000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F12201105%2Fimage-1733.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-response-to-south-africas-gaza-genocide-case-at-icj%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Israel%20told%20the%20ICJ%20that%20it%20was%20acting%20in%20self-defence%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20was%20fighting%20Hamas%2C%20not%20the%20Palestinian%20population.%20It%20urged%20the%20court%20to%20dismiss%20the%20case%20as%20groundless%20and%20reject%20South%20Africa's%20request%20to%20order%20a%20halt%20to%20the%20offensive.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisraels-response-to-south-africas-gaza-genocide-case-at-icj%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Google%20to%20add%20more%20real-money%20game%20apps%20on%20Play%2C%20charge%20a%20service%20fee%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1705070374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F07%2Ffull%2F1699337232-3946.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgoogle-to-add-more-real-money-game-apps-on-play-charge-a-service-fee-124011200877_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20%26quot%3Bexpanded%20RMG%20support%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20launched%20in%20June%20for%20developers%20in%20India%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Brazil%2C%20with%20plans%20to%20extend%20the%20service%20to%20more%20countries%20later%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2